        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0636P0_20020624_GCR_43' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        4.45 p.m.
      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0636P0-03730'>
        <a name='S5LV0636P0_20020624_GCR_44'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-philip-hunt' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0636P0_20020624_GCR_44' title='Link to this speech by Mr Philip Hunt' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
