            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_35gc' title='Col. 35GC &mdash; HL Deb 24 June 2002 vol 636 c35GC' name='column_35gc' href='#column_35gc' rel='bookmark'>35GC</a>
            which the right reverend Prelate has not had an opportunity to read. So I am making no criticism, and I am certainly not excusing myself. I thank all noble Lords who took part in the debate. I beg leave to withdraw the amendment.</p><p>
            Amendment, by leave, withdrawn.
          </p>
