            It is all based around a proper assessment. Clause 4(9) states:
            <q>If at any time during the assessment of the needs of any person under the section, it appears to a local authority that",</q>
            they need either health or LEA provision, they,
            <q>must notify the Health Authority, Primary Care Trust, or local education authority",</q>
            accordingly.</p><p>
